### 2. Missing security middleware
- No `helmet()` — responses ship without standard security headers (`X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, CSP, etc.).
- No rate limiting (`express-rate-limit`) — `/users` and `/health` can be trivially abused.
