- No body-size limit set on `express.json()` (if/when you add it) — default is 100kb but should be set explicitly.

### 3. No input validation
- Routes don't take input yet, but there's no validation library wired up (e.g., `zod`, `joi`, or `express-validator`). Add the scaffolding before adding the first parameterized route (`/users/:id`, search query, POST body).
