### 5. Server hardening
- `app.listen(3000, ...)` hardcodes the port — use `process.env.PORT` with a validated fallback.
- No `app.disable('x-powered-by')` (helmet does this, but worth noting).
- No graceful shutdown on `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` — in-flight requests get killed on deploy.
