| P1 | Remove PII (`email`) from `/users` or gate behind auth | Least-privilege data exposure |
| P2 | `process.env.PORT`, graceful shutdown, signal handlers | Production-grade lifecycle |
| P2 | Structured logging (`pino`), request IDs | Incident response |
