For testability, export `app` from one module and `listen()` from another (e.g., `server.js`). Right now `require('./app')` starts a listener as a side effect — problematic in tests.

## 10. Use structured logging

`console.log` is fine for hello-world, but switch to `pino` or `winston` with request IDs (e.g., via `pino-http`) before production. Never log request bodies that may contain secrets or PII.

