| Priority | Item | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| High | #1, #2, #8, #9 | Prevent crashes / info leaks today |
| High | #3 (helmet) | One-liner, broad protection |
| Medium | #4, #5, #12 | Become critical as the app grows |
| Medium | #6 | PII hygiene |
| Low | #7, #10, #11 | Future-proofing |

