| `x-powered-by` leak | Present | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| Hardcoded port | Present | `process.env.PORT` |
| Graceful shutdown | Missing | Handle SIGTERM/SIGINT |
| Testability | Weak | Only `listen()` when run directly, not on import |

