1. Error + 404 middleware and process handlers (prevents crashes / info leaks).
2. `helmet`, rate limiting, CORS allowlist, disable `x-powered-by`.
3. Validation layer (zod/joi) — establish before adding input-accepting routes.
4. Body size limits, structured logging, graceful shutdown.
5. AuthZ and PII minimization on `/users`.

