| Area | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| Security headers | None | `helmet()` + `x-powered-by` disabled |
| Rate limiting | None | `express-rate-limit` (100/15min) |
| Input validation | None | `express-validator` on query/body |
| Body size | Unbounded | Capped at 10 KB |
| Error responses | Could leak stack | Generic for 5xx, sanitized for 4xx |
| PII exposure | Email returned unauthenticated | Removed pending auth |
| Process safety | Crashes silently | `unhandledRejection` + `uncaughtException` hooks |
| Shutdown | Drops in-flight requests | Graceful `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` handling |
| Port conflict | Unhandled | `server.on('error')` handler |
| Config | Hardcoded port | `process.env.PORT` |

## Recommended `package.json` additions
```bash
npm i helmet express-rate-limit express-validator
```

